<div class="col tertiary-content">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-1">Accessibility</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Braille translation service<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled WC<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Induction loop<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Text Relay<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Signing service available<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Wheelchair access<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Step free access<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContentcf2a4056e19e4065a0abc92f1d55be76">
</div>
<p>Information and consultations can be provided for all needs.  GPs can state on referral and the hospital can access external services for patients.</p>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-2">Accommodation</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Access to TV<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="no">Internet access<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Public telephone<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="no">Family accommodation<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Mobile phones permitted<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="no">Private rooms only<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Single sex accommodation only<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent542174285a074992b4e70feaefa78ba1">
</div>
<p>The trust has paid for bedside TV (Hospedia). Mobile phones are permitted in specific areas and the trust meets same-sex guidelines.  In ITU and HDU critically ill male and female patients are nursed with privacy curtains.  One parent is able to stay with children on the paediatric ward (camp beds available)</p>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-3">Bringing children to Chesterfield Royal Hospital</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Baby changing facility<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="no">Children's play area<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="no">Parent and child parking<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Parent and baby room<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="no">Pram park<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContentb27ec7447f6044a1b16475183b96d47c">
</div>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-4">Counselling and Support</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Bereavement support<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Translation services<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent23746d6ad8aa46fb9845eb85ab0c7705">
</div>
<p>The trust has a dedicated bereavement service and offers translation services as requested.</p>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-6">Food and amenities on-site</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Cafe<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="no">Patient library<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Pharmacy<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Shop<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent14f78ad08dfb47238a4ef89cf031c1e9">
</div>
<p>The Royal runs its own catering outlets - with several on site (including one in partnership with the WRVS) offering a range of hot and cold snacks and meals.  All food is home-cooked and sourced from local suppliers (50 mile radius).<br/>The on-site pharmacy deals with in-patient and out-patient prescriptions; as well as GP prescriptions (for staff and members of the public).  The Pharmacy@theRoyal shop offers everyday medicines - and is available for staff, patients and the general public.</p>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-7">Parking</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Car Parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Cycle parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContentc734e264988c4eee859fa6d3f5241213">
</div>
<p>Blue badge parking is available at the front of the hospital.  Pay on exit secure, barrier controlled car parking is across the site - for staff, patients and visitors.  Cycle parking is available at the front entrance for members of the public.</p>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
